 (WF_REL_TAC `measure (logic_term_size o SND)` \\ SRW_TAC [] []
  THEN1 (Induct_on `vs` \\ SRW_TAC [] [MEM,logic_term_size_def] \\ RES_TAC \\ DECIDE_TAC)
  THEN1 (Induct_on `ys` \\ SRW_TAC [] [MEM,logic_term_size_def] \\ RES_TAC \\ DECIDE_TAC)
